ID:23
Summary: After adding  a new league with an existing name average score duplicated from the first league

Severity (Critical, Major, Medium, Minor):Minor
Description: Average score is duplicated in new league with existing name of leagues
 
Requirement ID:56
Reproducibility: always
Reproduced on: Android 10

Steps to reproduce:
1.Open QA Battle Score
2.Click [Add League]
3.Enter any league name
4.Click [add game]
5.Enter any game score
6. Click [Add League]
7.Enter the same league name
Actual result: average score is duplicated

Expected result: average score is 0



ID:15
Summary:  Status:413 Request Entity Too Large when username- valid max  characters length  and strict: false in body request 

Severity (Critical, Major, Medium, Minor): Medium
Description: Search request when username- valid max  characters length, server is not able to process and display Status:413 Request Entity Too Large
Reproducibility: always
Workaround:

Steps to reproduce:
1.Choose method Post
2. Paste Url: http://178.124.206.52/app/ws/
3. Choose content-Type: application/json
4.Paste in Body:
{"user»: rangaradjangoo",
"strict”: false}
5.Click [Send] button

Actual result: Status:413 Request Entity Too Large

Expected result: Status:200 OK
Operation status code: 0
All users by partial  username are listed with the following attributes:"id","username","realname","password" and "email"




